aland, Norway, Spain, Sweden, Switzerland and the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland Office at Geneva addressed to the President of the Human Rights Council|newspaper=[[聯合國人權理事會|聯合國人權理事會]]A/HRC/41/G/11文件|date=2019-07-08|last=澳洲、奧地利、比利時、加拿大、丹麥、愛沙尼亞、芬蘭、法國、德國、冰島、愛爾蘭、日本、拉脫維亞、立陶宛、盧森堡、荷蘭、紐西蘭、挪威、西班牙、瑞典、瑞士、英國|first=|url=https://documents-dds-ny.un.org/doc/UNDOC/GEN/G19/223/89/PDF/G1922389.pdf?OpenElement|archiveurl=http://web.archive.org/web/20190915124047/https://ap.ohchr.org/Documents/E/HRC/c_gov/A_HRC_41_G_11.DOCX|archivedate=2019-09-15}}</ref><ref name="50 countries Qatar">{{cite news|title=Annex to the letter dated 12 July 2019 from the representatives of Algeria, Angola, Bahrain, Bangladesh, Belarus, the Plurinational State of Bolivia, Burkina Faso, Burundi, Cambodia, Cameroon, Comoros, the Congo, Cuba, the Democratic People’s Republic of Korea, the Democratic Republic of the Congo, Djibouti, Egypt, Equatorial Guinea, Eritrea, Gabon, the Islamic Republic of Iran, Iraq, Kuwait, the Lao People’s Democratic Republic, Mozambique, Myanmar, Nepal, Nigeria, Oman, Pakistan, the Philippines, the Russian Federation, Saudi Arabia, Serbia, Somalia, South Sudan, Sri Lanka, the Sudan, the Syrian Arab Republic, Tajikistan, Togo, Turkmenistan, Uganda, the United Arab Emirates, Uzbekistan, the Bolivarian Republic of Venezuela, Yemen, Zambia, Zimbabwe and the State of Palestine to the United Nations Office at Geneva addressed to the President of the Human Rights Council|newspaper=[[聯合國人權理事會|聯合國人權理事會]]A/HRC/41/G/17文件|date=2019-07-12|last=|first=|url=https://ap.ohchr.org/Documents/E/HRC/c_gov/A_HRC_41_G_17.DOCX|archiveurl=http://web.archive.org/web/20190915124108/https://ap.ohchr.org/Documents/E/HRC/c_gov/A_HRC_41_G_17.DOCX|archivedate=2019-09-15}}</ref>

