==指控及反驳==
===維吾爾人出生率下降與「绝育和避孕」的關係===
2020年6月，德國學者[[阿德里安·曾兹|阿德里安·曾兹]]（又譯鄭國恩）发表了题为《结扎、宫内节育器和强制性计划生育》（''Sterilizations, IUDs, and Mandatory Birth Control''）的调查，<ref>{{cite journal|authorlink1=阿德里安·曾兹 |last1=Zenz |first1=Adrian |title=Sterilizations, IUDs, and Coercive Birth Prevention: The CCP’s Campaign to Suppress Uyghur Birth Rates in Xinjiang|url=https://jamestown.org/program/sterilizations-iuds-and-mandatory-birth-control-the-ccps-campaign-to-suppress-uyghur-birth-rates-in-xinjiang/ |journal=China Brief|volume=20|issue=12}}</ref>指出新疆自然人口增长急剧下降，認為原因是强制[[節育|節育]]措施；2020年10月他的續作補充了2019年的數據。<ref>{{cite web |authorlink1=阿德里安·曾兹 |last1=Zenz |first1=Adrian |title=A Response to the Report Compiled by Lin Fangfei, Associate Professor at Xinjiang University |url=https://adrianzenz.medium.com/a-response-to-the-report-compiled-by-lin-fangfei-associate-professor-at-xinjiang-university-bdad4bbb97f9 |website=Medium |publisher=Medium |accessdate=2021-02-25 |language=en |date=2020-10-16}}</ref>。一些維吾爾女性亦以親歷者身份向媒體供述，她們被餵[[絕育|绝育]]和[[避孕|避孕]]的藥物和疫苖。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=China's Forced Sterilization of Uighur Women Is Cultural Genocide|url=https://www.heritage.org/asia/commentary/chinas-forced-sterilization-uighur-women-cultural-genocide|accessdate=2019-12-02|author=Enos|date=2019-08-29|first=Olivia|work=The Heritage Foundation|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191202230646/https://www.heritage.org/asia/commentary/chinas-forced-sterilization-uighur-women-cultural-genocide|archivedate=2019-12-02}}</ref>[[美联社|美联社]]認為這是「限制[[中國穆斯林|中國穆斯林]]人口的[[德拉古|德拉古]]式政策」。<ref name="apne_Chin">{{Cite web|title=China cuts Uighur births with IUDs, abortion, sterilization|url=https://apnews.com/article/269b3de1af34e17c1941a514f78d764c|accessdate=2020-12-18|author=|date=2020-06-28|agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216200613/https://apnews.com/article/269b3de1af34e17c1941a514f78d764c|archivedate=2020-12-16|quote=The Chinese government is taking draconian measures to slash birth rates among Uighurs and other minorities as part of a sweeping campaign to curb its Muslim population}}</ref><ref name="apne_Chin"/><ref name="bbc">{{Cite news|date=2020-06-29|title=China 'using birth control' to suppress Uighurs|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-53220713|accessdate=2020-07-07|archivedate=2020-06-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200629222610/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-53220713}}</ref>

